Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how hard you've\Nbeen working lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured you\Ncould use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, this looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But my job doesn't\Nreally seem like work...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, being counselor\Nfor the students
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,at Twilight's School of\NFriendship is demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but... [chimes] Oh, one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I saying? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to use\Nthe experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of my checkered past\Nto help young students
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,feels pretty great.\NOooh! Yum! Mm. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I feel\Nnothing but admiration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for the work you do, but it\Nis a little all-consuming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and I miss spending\Ntime with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're spending\Ntime right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought!\N[poof]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[poof] Hah! Sorry. I cast a spell\Non the door to my office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so this bracelet goes off\Nwhenever there's a knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona is having the worst\Ntime with her braids lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally respect my\Nyounger cousins' decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay seaponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but they've never\Nbeen on dry land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing for a visit with\Nthem is almost as much work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as the research assignment\NHeadmare Twilight gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,on Hazardous Fauna of\Nthe Everfree Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How would {\i1}you{\i0} describe\Na shower to creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who live in water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, I've got\Nwarm and steamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, steam\Nhas water in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream, there\Nare a lot of students
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who want to see me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a few\Nshower adjectives
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that don't rely\Non the wet part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Well, there's\Nclean, relaxing, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Relaxing? I don't know.\NA nap's relaxing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm and clean are OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I have to give\Nthis some more thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. OK. Well, I'm here to\Nhelp. My door's always open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for today, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave now, we\Ncan finish everything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,before sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, I can't leave!\NIt's almost Spring Break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight and the others\Nhave already left
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate the Spring\NSolstice in Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have to help the\Nstudents with any issues
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,before they head\Nhome for the holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're busy, but I\Nhope you haven't forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about the Spring Sols-tastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The party Maud and\NMudbriar are throwing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst is coming to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I promised\Nto make the cake..?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh PFFFT! How could I possibly\Nforget about that..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony is saying your\Njob isn't important,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but plans you make with your\Nfriends are important too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I know. I'm sorry. I\Nshouldn't have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I need to be\Navailable to my students,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT! That doesn't\Nmean I can't help
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the things\Nwe have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what {\i1}are{\i0} all the\Nthings we have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud needs streamers\Nfor the decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst wants us to pick up\Na genuine, pre-Equestrian,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring Solstice chafing\Ndish from the antique shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mudbriar wants a "bouquet\Nof flowering sticks,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought we were BOTH\Nlooking forward to Mrs. Cake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching us the secret recipe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to her famous Spring\NSolstice cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I totally am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. we could just buy\Na cake from her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We could, but then we'd\Nmiss out on baking {\i1}together{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus the time I spent\Nflattering and convincing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and begging her to share the\Nrecipe would be for NOTHING,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we promised to MAKE\Na cake, not BUY a cake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great and powerful\NTrixie keeps her promises!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Why don't we just\Nsplit up these jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the streamers\Nand the chafing dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You ... [chiming] get\Nstarted on those sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, why don't I\Njust hang onto this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to forget\Nthe things I just said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am TOTALLY going\Nto take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be plum blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[poof] Wha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Sorry Rose,\Nbut I need a bouquet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of flowering sticks, STAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was getting\Nthe flowering sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm still not exactly\Nsure what they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the sticks;\NI'll get the streamers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,right after I take\Ncare of what I am sure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is an even smaller student\Nproblem than the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!\N[poof]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have the shower\Nthing under control,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't figure out\Nhow to describe a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Smolder, I\Nunderstand the school
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,can be a bit drafty,\Nbut that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can breathe fire\Nanywhere you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean Trixie already\Npicked up Sunburst's genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,pre-Equestrian,\NEquine-ox chafing dish!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my job...! I\Nthink. Wait. Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus, it's perfectly\Nnormal for a changeling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to struggle with\Nidentity issues, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor Starlight?\NWhen you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some synonyms\Nfor the word "dry."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or really just help\Nexplaining the concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[poof] Oh, wait! Mrs. Cake!\NYou can't close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie and I need\Nto learn the recipe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for your Equine-ox cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine, dear.\NTrixie was already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her everything\Nshe needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? NO! Ah! The Great\Nand Powerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,might keep her promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but the busy and distracted\NStarlight sure doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised to help her today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't done\Na single thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that does\Nsound hard, dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not sure quite\Nhow to tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but.. your hoof\Nis glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie!? What are\Nyou doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one place I\Nknew I could find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry about\Ntoday. I'm just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, your students\Nare more important
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,than your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...\N[knocking]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,\NSilverstream, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I need to lock up\Nthe school for the holiday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's time you\Ncaught the train home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a smart and\Ncapable student like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,can figure out the solution to\Nany problem over the break,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but for now, the counselor's\Noffice is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a cake to bake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Is this cake\Nsupposed to be so sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it looks\Nreally... interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, it's\Nnot symmetrical
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or aesthetically pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not the best cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but we made it together\Nand that's what counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you brought\Nit, and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the\Nmost perfect party ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And with all of your students\Nhome for the holiday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have to worry\Nabout you being summoned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to your office in\Nthe middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm! Nothing is going to take\Nme away from this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!? Starlight? Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is a\Nprivate cavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Starlight here!? I\Nwas told she'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Terramar,\NSilverstream's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking\Nall over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream didn't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm. I was supposed to meet her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Mount Aris train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but she never showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long way between\NPonyville and Mount Aris.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parents are leading\Nteams of hippogriffs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and seaponies, searching\Nthe land and sea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,between here and our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They sent me to\Ncheck the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But the school's closed!\NAll the students are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she had a big\Nproject due for Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she might\Nhave stayed to finish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She never told me\Nabout a project...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you closed your office\Nthe last time she came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really..?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,turns away a student\Nwith a problem!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind with too\Nmuch on her plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight has always\Ngone out of her way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for her students.\NAnd I mean, {\i1}ALWAYS{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Except apparently\Nwhen it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You all go back\Nto the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Terramar and I will\Ncheck the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known\Nit couldn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Party perfection is\Nmore of a "Pinkie" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. I wasn't going to\Nsay anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but these flowers\Nare just glued on so,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,technically it wasn't\Nperfect already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's probably\Nnot important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You check the grounds\Nand I'll look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[echo] Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anycreature!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you check her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she isn't. But look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A cockatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be what\Nher project was on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think she went\Ninto the Everfree Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to find a Cockatrice\Nby herself, do you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I'm\Ngoing to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[poof] Ha ha! [poof]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What are you\Nall doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't let you\Nhandle this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, she\Nwasn't alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but we wanted to help anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but the students are\Nmy responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who\Ndidn't do my job
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when it actually\Nmattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I might share a\Nbit of the blame
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for pressuring you into\Nleaving work early...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want\Nto ruin your party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still\Nhave a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A search party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we talk about\Nall this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream might be in\Nthe Everfree Forest alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We think she went in to do\Nresearch on Cockatrices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? The gaze of the\Ncockatrice is known
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to petrify any who\Ndare to cross its path!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reptilian birds\Nare elusive and solitary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would we even start!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} have a lot of\Nexperience telling ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have experience with\Nthe dangerous creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of Everfree Forest. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [adventurous music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The great and directionally\Nastute Trixie says
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we go left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [music fades out] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we just here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, do have {\i1}any{\i0} idea\Nhow to find a Cockatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But usually when\Nthere's a dangerous creature
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in the forest I\Ndon't want to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,this is how I meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We might need a\Nmore concrete plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, according to\NSilverstream's research,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}the Cockatrice prefers rocky{\i0}\N{\i1} terrain and ample shade{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocks and shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I can't imagine where\Nwe'll find THAT in a forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, rocks aren't the\Nmost hospitable environment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for shade trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, pine\Ntrees like Pinus Cembra
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or Pinus Sylvestris can\Ngrow from narrow crevasses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or cracks in a\Nrocky rhizosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You complete me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some pine\Ntrees over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said\Nthey were solitary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They are! This must be\Nsome kind of migration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! At least there's no\Nsign of Silverstream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine getting caught
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of that flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just lucky\Nwe're all over here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're all over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do,\Ndon't look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Their gaze can\Nturn you to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[poof] Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight! I'm so sorry!\NWe have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream might\Nstill be in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here. I'll get the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The clucking is coming\Nfrom everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful\NTrixie fears no cluck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Maud! We've got to\Nget out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Mudbriar's been turned to stone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I could\Nlove him any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't\Nfound Silverstream;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't leave yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope Silverstream\Nfound a good place to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be hundreds more\NCockatrices on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If this really is a migration,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll take a full lunar\Ncycle to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I have to get word\Nback to our parents
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that Silverstream\Ncould be surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by those terrifying birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And as handsome as\NMudbriar is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we should probably\Ncatch one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn him back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,UGH! This IS all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never taking time off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,from my counseling duties again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems a little extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!? If I hadn't galloped\Noff to a holiday celebration,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream would be\Nsafe with her family
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'd all be\Nenjoying Maud's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, my student is missing;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we're surrounded by a flock\Nof petrifying.. chicken-snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And Maud's boyfriend was\Nturned into a hunk of rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the hunk part right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And to top it off, we have\N{\i1}no{\i0} idea if Silverstream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,even came to Everfree at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no idea\Nwhere else to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Has that always been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh. That's the\Nstudents' Treehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it grew from\Nthe Tree of Harmony and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That should have been the\Nfirst place we looked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Silverstream, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor Starlight, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Edith. She's\Nhelping me with my project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I.. don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After you encouraged me\Nto solve my own problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to get my\Nproject done {\i1}before{\i0} I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I could really\Nfocus on my family
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,during my visit. The school\Nwas closed so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are worried sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Edith volunteered to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockatrice's are really friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know how to\Ninteract with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how to trigger her\Nnesting response.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They are really\Nfascinating creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that they migrate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Everfree\NForest once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you {\i1}imagine{\i0}\Nwhat would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you stumbled on a\Nwhole flock of these!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a few ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you got turned\Nto stone looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm glad Edith was\Nable to turn you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you tell the difference..?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have mixed feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, I will\Nalways be a stick pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but the experience has given me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,an even deeper appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for the density and\Npermanence of rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Swoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream and I\Nshould get going,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything you\Ndid to help find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish I\Nhadn't abandoned her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, you\Ndidn't abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I might as well have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though it\Nturned out all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,things could have\Nbeen a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be expected to\Nsupervise your students
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,every second of every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that you're\Nalways available,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it kind of makes\Nit OK to come to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with stuff that maybe\Nisn't {\i1}super{\i0} important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, being a\Nschool counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is a big responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but always being at work\Nisn't fair to anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think if I had\Nset times to see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it might help you decide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what you really\Nneed to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, you really\Nweren't very helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with the other stuff anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Wait, what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Spring\NSols-tastic, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants a piece of\NMrs. Cake's famous--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst: Petrified dessert!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You had me\Nat "petrified".
